## Working with GSD

GSD is the main project management system. When working in a project with `.planning/`:
- Use `/gsd:resume-work` at session start to restore context
- The GSD executor manages atomic commits and checkpoints
- Don't create manual project structure if GSD can manage it
- GSD agents (gsd-planner, gsd-executor, etc.) are the correct ones for planning/execution

